COVID-19 Status 💉 🦠

As of 8:21AM PT today, over 1.4 million Canadians have tested positive for COVID-19. Sadly, 25.1 thousand have died.

In the last day, 662 new infections were reported and 8 deaths. This is trending downwards.

Fortunately, 19.7 million doses of the vaccine have been administered. For those 12 years and older, 54.7% have their 1st shot and 4.6% are fully vaccinated!

Vaccination is speeding up, but there are 2.6 million doses in the freezer. It currently takes ~7 days for new deliveries to get into arms. At the current rate, all Canadians aged 12+ should have the first dose by Jul-08 and fully vaccinated by Sep-02. There is no approved vaccine for children aged 11 or younger.
